p: The electrospinning fibers were prepared using a single-capillary spinneret with a feed rate of 0.8 mL h −1. PS was mixed in solution of chlorobenzene (CB), and dimethyl sulfoxide (DMSO) with different ratios, followed by magnetic stirring at 50 °C for 12 h. All the experiments were carried out at room temperature, a humidity of 50%–70%, and an applied voltage of 14 kV.
